    "pages.privacy.title": "Gopniyata Niti",
    "pages.privacy.content": "Aapki privacy hamare liye mahatvapurn hai.\n\nData Sangrah:\nHum naam ya email jaisi niji jankari ikatha nahi karte. Hum site ki performance behtar banane ke liye anonymous analytics (jaise cookies) ka upyog kar sakte hain.\n\nVideo Storage Nahi:\nSaveTikFast apne servers par koi video host ya store nahi karta. Sabhi file processing turant hoti hai.",
